SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT cast (sum(CMON_N:9LIMREQPRELIM) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_N:9LIMREQRFD) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_N:9LIMREQRFDPRELIM) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_N:9LIMREQINFREQ) as decimal (13,2)) FROM :1 where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_CURRENCY=':4' and CMON_YEAR between :5 and :6 and CMON_MONTH between :7 and :8 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows

select CLCR_NO, CLCR_ADMNO, CLCR_CLNTNO, CLCR_REQSTATUS, CLCR_COUNTRY, CLCR_DEBH_NO, CLCR_AMOUNT, CLCR_CURRENCYREQ, CLCR_DATE, CLCR_URGENT from :1 where CLCR_ADMNO = :2 and CLCR_CLNTNO = :3 and CLCR_TYPE = ':4' and CLCR_REQSTATUS between 1 and 4 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
